    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Space Diner Simulator is a cozy diner management game where you will slowly grow your diner from a humble little place to a place with many workers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook, clean, serve and unlock new recipes as you improve your diner with all kinds of different equipment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/d71c1971c521d9b8864782c8648a7bf4.avif?t=1770930995\" width=620 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quality service is of the utmost importance in the hospitality service. Customers will complain if the food isn't on time or if it's not hot enough. So speed is greatly appreciated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/47d14dda0a9c094e3958bcbfd67af76a.poster.avif?t=1770930995\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/47d14dda0a9c094e3958bcbfd67af76a.webm?t=1770930995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/47d14dda0a9c094e3958bcbfd67af76a.mp4?t=1770930995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/2f515a04cad88f3de05091a2ceb2cb69.avif?t=1770930995\" width=620 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooking is a skill and as any skill over time it gets better. The more dishes you prepare, the better quality and price they will have. But don't be afraid to try all the different dishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/31782e156b50780b8a81bd24eaa9fb16.poster.avif?t=1770930995\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/31782e156b50780b8a81bd24eaa9fb16.webm?t=1770930995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/31782e156b50780b8a81bd24eaa9fb16.mp4?t=1770930995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/183e4e8e935cdb165f997aa4a7cc31e5.avif?t=1770930995\" width=620 height=70 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Organize your workspace so that it serves your needs perfectly. Organization and efficiency is everything when running a diner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/a14d4e35c2e6d070e2ed4e3fd1b9b6ca.poster.avif?t=1770930995\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/a14d4e35c2e6d070e2ed4e3fd1b9b6ca.webm?t=1770930995\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312040/extras/a14d4e35c2e6d070e2ed4e3fd1b9b6ca.mp4?t=1770930995\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
